author: Inside Edition
description: The UN's International Atomic Energy Agency made a troubling announcement on Friday: Chernobyl's protective shield is no longer working. The containment hangar was meant to seal in radioactive material from the nuclear plant's Number 4 reactor. But after a drone armed with heavy explosives struck the shield in February of 2025, the structure suffered heavy damages. Ukraine said Russia is responsible for the drone attack, a charge that Russia denies.
title: Chernobyl's Protective Shield Isn't Working After Drone Strike

author: Inside Edition
description: A popular food influencer, reportedly killed by police in Texas last month, had shared his mental health struggles with his followers just weeks before his death. Michael Duarte was known to his millions of followers as Food With Bear Hands. He amassed a large fan base with his over-the-top recipes. On October 25, he posted a personal story on Instagram about having a mental breakdown. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Influencer Shared Mental Health Struggle Before He Was Killed by Cops: Reports
